      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KEEP ROLLING (1) was out of the placings last time when fifth at this track (30.20) but scored four back at Warrnambool (25.42). Solid record here at the distance winning three races. Looks the one to beat on his best form. NEO DEVERE (4) shapes well for this on his powerful win a few runs back, getting around Horsham over 485m in 27.10 then hitting the frame in both runs since. Expecting another bold showing. PAW QWAN (8) jumped from a low draw and boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten half a length (30.07) behind Paw Quinby at this track. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Can measure up. READY ONE (7) comes off a (29.42) win last time, scoring by 2.25 lengths in a Grade 5 H over 515m at Sandown. Loves this draw, having won three of five starts.",
